/1080_1080.jpg" alt="「幸せになれない結婚相談所 【分冊版】」 紹介画像"></div></a></article><style>.classicComic_typeC2{margin:10px;border:2px solid #000;border-radius:5px}.classicComic_typeC2_mainImage{padding:5px;border-bottom:2px #fff dashed;background:#333}.classicComic_typeC2_inn{overflow:hidden;padding:5px;position:relative}.classicComic_typeC2_left_img{width:65px;margin-right:5px;float:left}.classicComic_typeC2_right_detail{overflow:hidden;min-height:75px}.classicComic_typeC2_catch{background:#dc3057;padding:3px;color:#fff;font-weight:bold;line-height:1.3;border-radius:5px}.classicComic_typeC2_btn{position:absolute;right:5px;bottom:5px;color:#004cff}.classicComic_typeC2_btn::after{content:'\f101';margin-left:5px;font-family:"icomoon",sans-serif}</style><style>.link_more_bottom__ico_allStar_cam::before{content:"\e903"}.txtBtn_first{display:block;background:#ff8c00;padding:4px;text-align:center;color:#fff;border-radius:4px;font-size:.7rem;border-bottom:1px solid #aaa;margin-top:2px}.contentsBox_fastComic .contentsBox_fcspcam{margin:5px;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;border:2px solid #333}.contentsBox_fcspcam .box_ttl::before{background:#fc0;content:"\f219";color:#fff;line-height:24px;text-align:center}.contentsBox_fcspcam .box_ttl::after{border-left:20px solid #fc0}.contentsBox_fcspcam_inrTtl{padding:5px;font-size:1.2em;font-weight:bold;background:#333;color:#fff}</style><div class="contentsBox_fastComic_inn"><div class="comic_displayTile"><!-- 10/9 SNS狂の --><div class="basic_comicList_item"><a href="/sd/page/title/0000cgcp/" class="shadow"><p class="basic_comicList_topLabel">10/9 新刊</p><img src="/sd/image/title/240/0000cgcp.jpg" alt="SNS狂の女"><p class="comicList_ttl"><span class="txt_comicTtl">SNS狂の女</span></p></a></div>
